title: [Endeltime Estates, The Crossing]
description: Twin rows of skeletal trees line each side of the crossroads, their gnarled branches perched with dozens of crows, each one gazing down at the sigil-covered ground.  The faint cry high above reveals a duo of vultures, the predators circling lower with each flap of their wings above a circle of empty buildings.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
